featuredItems.itemDescription: The King of Loaded BoxesRich, grass-fed Angus beef mince layered over crispy seasoned fries, smothered in velvety cheese sauce, and melted red and white cheddar. Topped with our signature Algerian sauce, fiery mixed chillies, and a fresh garnish—this is bold, beefy indulgence at its finest. No shortcuts, no compromises—just maximum flavour, full stop.

featuredItems.title: Chicken Shawarma
featuredItems.itemDescription: Juicy slices of chicken shaved fresh from our signature shawarma stack, marinated overnight in bold Middle Eastern spices. Grilled to perfection with that irresistible flame-roasted flavour—this is shawarma done the Chickeez way: tender, smoky, and packed with attitude.

featuredItems.title: Butter Chicken Shawarma
featuredItems.itemDescription: Sliced straight from our signature shawarma stack, Chickeez chicken meets rich, creamy tikka sauce in this desi-inspired twist. Tossed with sautéed onions, fresh coriander, and finished with a smooth drizzle of fresh cream, the Butter Chicken Shawarma is pure comfort with a bold, smoky edge.

featuredItems.title: Wings
featuredItems.itemDescription: Golden, crunchy, and straight-up addictive. These fried wings are crispy on the outside, tender inside, and ready to be dipped, dunked, or devoured.

featuredItems.title: Chickeez Butter Chicken
featuredItems.itemDescription: Homemade curry sauce base, cheese, tandoori chicken, red onion, mixed pepper, green chilli, jalapeño, and a drizzle of coriander sauce.

featuredItems.title: Hot Fried Chicken Loaded
featuredItems.itemDescription: Crispy shredded chicken laid over fries and smothered in our homemade cheese sauce, layered with red and white cheddar, and hit with a fiery drizzle of hot honey buffalo. Finished with ranch, jalapeños, and a fresh garnish—this one brings the perfect balance of heat, creaminess, and crunch. A loaded box for those who like it loud.

featuredItems.title: Sweet Chilli Chicken Loaded
featuredItems.itemDescription: Crispy shredded chicken stacked high on golden fries, smothered in rich cheese sauce and a blend of red and white cheddar. Drizzled with sweet chilli sauce and our homemade ranch, then finished with a fresh garnish—this loaded box hits the perfect sweet-and-savoury spot with every bite.

We cannot guarantee that cross contact with meat products will not occur.
